descriptionNullable:
Stock data time series with 20 day log of stock return value and other datapoints from technical analysis.

Dataset file details are as below.
It contains two csv files which are train.csv - Training File and test.csv - Testing File
Train file contains 2247 rows of data.
Test file contains 502 rows of data.

The columns are described below
Columns:
date: This column represents the date for each data point.
twenty_day_stock_log_return: This column gives the daily or periodic return on a stock over the past 20 days or 20-Day Log of Stock Return Value.
Datapoint_1,..,Datapoint_209: Other Technical Indicators, These are columns containing technical indicators used for financial analysis.
